    <div class="container why-inner">
      <h2>How High Indoor Humidity<br />Affects Your Home</h2>
      <p class="why-intro">Excess indoor moisture can lead to mold growth, structural wood damage, poor air quality, and increased HVAC strain throughout the home.</p>
